messages.title: A strong team with SOLUTIONS FOR SCOTLAND
messages.content: By voting for the Scottish Liberal Democrats on your peach regional ballot paper on May 5th you'll be backing a strong team led by former MP Willie Rennie.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: The party prioritizes creating jobs as a part of their solution for Scotland.
The party focuses on support for the local police force.
The party aims for excellence in education.

issues.education: The party aims for excellence in education.
issues.environment: Scottish Liberal Democrats are offering solutions for Scotland. Restoring excellence in education, planning to get Scotland working again, keeping police local, and tackling climate change.

endorsements.endorsement: By voting for the Scottish Liberal Democrats on your peach regional ballot paper on May 5th you'll be backing a strong team led by former MP Willie Rennie. The more votes for Willie's team, the more MPs for our area together with me.

images.caption: Willie Rennie and Charles Kennedy MP with supporters.
